20:08.290 --> 20:09.996
Nathan.

20:10.126 --> 20:11.616
Nathan, what happened?
Where--

20:13.713 --> 20:14.919
Hey, where's Ray and Lilly?

20:15.047 --> 20:16.878
What's going on here?
Nathan!

20:18.884 --> 20:21.091
