- Oh, Nathan.

20:52.877 --> 20:54.413
What are you talking about?

20:54.545 --> 20:56.877
Whoa!

20:59.383 --> 21:00.714
- We've rounded up
the party boys.

21:00.843 --> 21:02.834
I'm still trying
to get a line on Nathan.

21:02.970 --> 21:07.054
- All right, we got to find out
what's causing this.

21:07.183 --> 21:09.139
- I can only think
of one common denominator.

21:09.268 --> 21:10.383
- What?

21:10.519 --> 21:12.350
- Not what, who.

21:18.194 --> 21:19.309
- Lilly.

21:19.445 --> 21:21.151
- Audrey, are you there, honey?

21:21.280 --> 21:24.067
I got a 20 on Nathan's car.
He's down at the marina.

21:24.200 --> 21:25.781
- Great.

21:40.716 --> 21:42.832
- [scoffs]
Look, Nathan.

21:45.137 --> 21:48.675
You may want to consider
switching to decaf, buddy.

21:48.808 --> 21:51.675
- What's it feel like--

21:51.811 --> 21:53.051
the sun?

21:54.104 --> 21:55.685
- Feels good.

22:00.903 --> 22:03.394
Hey!
What are you doing?

22:03.531 --> 22:05.487
- What's it like
to feel this?

22:05.616 --> 22:08.653
You talk about
the things I've done?

22:08.786 --> 22:10.868
It's nothing compared
to the things you've done!

22:10.996 --> 22:12.987
- Who?
- The things you still do!

22:14.750 --> 22:16.490
To me!

22:22.675 --> 22:25.166
