22:49.243 --> 22:50.574
- What's going on?

22:50.703 --> 22:52.785
- I need you
to keep him here.

22:52.913 --> 22:54.574
- No.

22:54.707 --> 22:56.288
- He's sick, Duke.

22:57.960 --> 22:59.075
- I knew that.

22:59.211 --> 23:00.371
- This is different, all right?

23:00.504 --> 23:01.664
Something--

23:01.797 --> 23:03.879
something
just happened to him.

