get to her soon,

23:15.144 --> 23:17.055
she's gonna make
more like him.

23:17.187 --> 23:18.768
Okay, so I got to go.

23:18.898 --> 23:20.604
- I'm not...

23:20.733 --> 23:23.816
- This is the part where you
come through for me, right?

23:23.944 --> 23:26.481
Remember who kept you
from going to jail?

23:36.415 --> 23:38.827
- l was having
such a nice day.

23:38.959 --> 23:41.450
- Officer Parker,
it's Dr. Lucassi.

23:41.587 --> 23:43.123
Any luck finding Lilly?

23:43.255 --> 23:44.631
- Not yet.

23:44.757 --> 23:47.294
Hey, can I
ask you something?

23:47.426 --> 23:50.293
When it all happened,
was Lilly playing the piano?

23:50.429 --> 23:52.545
- Yes, I seem to recall her

23:52.681 --> 23:54.296
actually starting
to play something.

23:54.433 --> 23:55.548
Why do you ask?

23:55.684 --> 23:56.890
- Well, according to Nathan,

23:57.019 --> 23:58.555
she was playing
at the Shiny Scupper too

23:58.687 --> 23:59.972
or, at least, you know,
trying to.

24:00.105 --> 24:01.481
- And?

24:01.607 --> 24:03.222
- At least
it's a common denominator.

24:03.359 --> 24:06.977
