I'm not a parasite.

24:55.160 --> 24:58.573
[laughing]

24:58.706 --> 25:00.571
- That's a good one.

25:02.835 --> 25:04.496
- Just using people...

25:07.631 --> 25:09.542
Like you always do.

25:09.675 --> 25:12.667
Are you planning
