he can own this nice of a boat.

25:55.596 --> 25:57.427
- Well, from what he's told me
during his visits,

25:57.556 --> 25:59.763
his grandfather abandoned it
when the McBreen family

25:59.892 --> 26:01.132
washed up in Haven years ago.

26:01.268 --> 26:02.428
[cell phone rings]

26:02.561 --> 26:04.426
- Sorry.
Excuse me.

26:04.563 --> 26:06.599
- No problem; I'll see
if I can locate the boat.

26:06.732 --> 26:08.017
- Okay.

26:08.150 --> 26:09.765
