playing Prince Charming.

26:23.957 --> 26:25.618
- Caught it,
didn't I?

26:25.751 --> 26:27.992
- How are you feeling?

26:29.755 --> 26:31.620
- I'm not sure
which is worse:

26:31.757 --> 26:35.716
going crazy
or being sane afterwards.

26:35.844 --> 26:38.836
- What do you remember?

26:38.972 --> 26:40.098
- Shiny Scupper.

26:40.224 --> 26:41.339
That's it.

26:41.475 --> 26:43.682
- Lilly was playing
the piano there.

26:46.146 --> 26:48.353
- Yeah.
Why?

26:48.482 --> 26:50.473
- I think her music
is causing this.

26:50.609 --> 26:53.021
- No, I don't think so.
- No, come on, Nathan.

26:53.153 --> 26:55.314
This is notjust me being
excited over the weirdness.

26:55.447 --> 26:58.689
- I didn't say it was.

26:58.826 --> 27:01.533
I just don't think it's Lilly
who's causing this.

27:01.662 --> 27:03.653
- Why?

27:03.789 --> 27:05.245
- Ray sat down next to her
at the piano,

27:05.374 --> 27:07.160
and he started to play.

27:07.292 --> 27:11.080
- Wait.
Ray did?

27:13.423 --> 27:15.880
- I got some music
for the trip:

27:16.009 --> 27:19.422
Aretha at the Fillmore
with Ray Charles,

27:19.555 --> 27:21.762
Spirit in the Dark.

27:25.519 --> 27:26.759
- Ray?

27:28.522 --> 27:30.183
What happened
to those people at the bar?

27:30.315 --> 27:33.478
That was awful.
Did I do that?

27:33.610 --> 27:35.316
- You?
No. No.

27:35.445 --> 27:37.481
- Did you?

27:37.614 --> 27:39.650
Oh, my God, Ray!

27:39.783 --> 27:41.489
- It's okay.
- It's not okay.

27:41.618 --> 27:44.030
You can't keep doing that.

27:45.497 --> 27:46.873
- Of course.

27:46.999 --> 27:50.662
Ray was at the Freddy.
I saw him on the tape.

27:50.794 --> 27:53.376
He must be the one
who changed all these people,

27:53.505 --> 27:55.837
but he left so fast
that he didn't even realize it.

27:55.966 --> 27:59.379
- Pretty sure he knows
what he's doing now.

27:59.511 --> 28:01.047
- Lil,

28:01.180 --> 28:03.091
I won't lose you again.

28:03.223 --> 28:04.554
- I don't want
to hurt people.

28:04.683 --> 28:06.548
- I don't want
to hurt people either.

28:11.064 --> 28:12.349
All right?

28:37.007 --> 28:38.713
- No word
on Lilly or Ray.

28:38.842 --> 28:40.924
I guess we got to go find
the Caprice.

28:41.053 --> 28:43.294
- I know
where the boat is.

28:43.430 --> 28:45.421
- Great.
Where?

28:45.557 --> 28:46.797
- I'll take you to her.

28:46.934 --> 28:48.720
- No.
It's just us.

28:50.646 --> 28:52.136
- Oh.

28:52.272 --> 28:53.682
Okay, forget it.

28:55.651 --> 28:56.936
we could throw you in jail.

28:57.069 --> 28:58.775
- No, you can't.

28:58.904 --> 29:01.520
And, frankly, I'm getting
a little sick of the threat.

29:01.657 --> 29:03.147
Considering
that a police officer

29:03.283 --> 29:04.489
just attacked me...

29:04.618 --> 29:06.950
- Mr. Crocker?

29:07.079 --> 29:09.161
I encourage you
to file a complaint

29:09.289 --> 29:11.780
and press charges.

29:13.210 --> 29:14.746
- [sighs]

29:16.546 --> 29:18.002
Not my style, Nathan.

29:18.131 --> 29:20.258
- Why exactly
do you want to come?

29:20.384 --> 29:23.501
- 'Cause I'm
a good citizen.

29:23.637 --> 29:28.051
And I want to know what
the hell's going on around here.

29:36.275 --> 29:38.641
- Okay, that should get
that head working,

29:38.777 --> 29:40.813
at least until we get
out of here.

29:40.946 --> 29:42.356
- [humming]

29:42.489 --> 29:44.980
- Damn.

29:45.117 --> 29:46.402
Hang in there, babe.
Hang in there.

29:46.535 --> 29:48.275
