- Hey, Ray.

30:40.672 --> 30:42.754
- It's you.

30:42.883 --> 30:44.874
- No!

30:45.010 --> 30:46.671
- No, no, no, no.
I'm coming.

30:46.803 --> 30:48.839
- No, the deal was, you have
to do exactly what we say.

30:48.972 --> 30:50.303
And I'm saying stay here.

30:50.432 --> 30:52.388
- Wait.

30:52.517 --> 30:54.178
- And the people
from the Scupper

30:54.311 --> 30:56.597
