the same time you did.

30:56.730 --> 30:58.345
- So people
who hear Ray together

30:58.482 --> 30:59.813
are affected
for the same duration.

30:59.941 --> 31:01.442
- Yeah, but you were gone
for two hours,

31:01.568 --> 31:03.479
and the people from the Freddy
were gone for four.

31:03.612 --> 31:05.193
- So what makes it shorter?

31:05.322 --> 31:09.281
- No, the better question is,
what makes it longer?

31:09.409 --> 31:12.901
- Okay, now I wish
Haven had a SWAT team.

31:13.038 --> 31:14.448
Whoa.

31:14.581 --> 31:17.744
Down. Down.
Down! Down.

31:20.379 --> 31:21.960
So what happened?

31:22.089 --> 31:24.705
- Lucassi overpowered Ray,
threw him in the car,

31:24.841 --> 31:27.093
and said something
about getting him back.

31:30.055 --> 31:31.886
Okay, you keep her here
until we call you.

31:32.015 --> 31:33.755
- Okay, you're taking
this good citizen thing

31:33.892 --> 31:35.553
way too literally!

31:37.437 --> 31:40.395
We're staying here, okay?

31:40.524 --> 31:42.560
- Lilly's sure
Lucassi came here?

31:42.692 --> 31:43.977
- Where else would he go?

31:44.111 --> 31:46.272
Since he knows
what Ray can do.

31:46.405 --> 31:48.896
Nathan, Lucassi
wants to help his patients

31:49.032 --> 31:50.192
more than anything.

31:50.325 --> 31:51.826
He's a good doctor.

31:51.952 --> 31:54.443
- And, presently,
crazier than an outhouse rat.

31:54.579 --> 31:57.412
- Yeah, well,
then there's that.

31:57.541 --> 31:59.452
You know, it might work.
- What?

31:59.584 --> 32:01.370
- The doctor using Ray
to help his patients--

32:01.503 --> 32:03.619
I mean, if he can manage him,
keep him safe.

32:03.755 --> 32:05.370
- That's a big if.

32:05.507 --> 32:07.543
Take it from a guy
who caught the funk.

32:10.220 --> 32:12.427
- You're right.

32:12.556 --> 32:15.548
[saw whirring]

32:18.019 --> 32:20.010
We might have
a problem.

32:33.285 --> 32:35.150
- Stop.

32:35.287 --> 32:36.652
This is sterile.

32:36.788 --> 32:40.280
- Okay. Okay.
Just--

32:40.417 --> 32:42.248
Doctor?

32:42.377 --> 32:43.537
Don't do this.

32:43.670 --> 32:45.661
- Do you realize
what this man can do?

32:45.797 --> 32:47.173
- Yes, yes.

32:47.299 --> 32:49.506
- I need his brain.

32:49.634 --> 32:52.967
This--this--this--

32:53.096 --> 32:54.597
this is a whole new world.

32:54.723 --> 32:58.511
- You're right.
We do need to understand him.

32:58.643 --> 33:01.385
- If we can.

33:01.521 --> 33:02.806
If we can.

33:04.858 --> 33:07.315
Been exploring the brain
for 20 years.

33:07.444 --> 33:09.730
20 years,
been exploring the brain.

33:09.863 --> 33:13.856
We can spare--we can spare
the families the pain

33:13.992 --> 33:17.200
