fade away to a--

33:17.329 --> 33:19.035
[electricity crackles]

33:22.542 --> 33:25.158
- You're getting good
at that.

33:25.295 --> 33:28.207
- Electricity:
it did--did wonders on you.

33:28.340 --> 33:30.046
- Uh-huh.

33:48.318 --> 33:52.106
- Ray,
I'm changing back.

33:52.239 --> 33:53.695
-lneed
a musical instrument.

33:53.823 --> 33:56.109
- No!
No music.

33:56.243 --> 33:57.358
- Lil.

33:57.494 --> 33:58.609
- No.

33:58.745 --> 34:00.736
- Why?
- Why?

34:00.872 --> 34:04.205
You were tied up, with a guy
about to open your head.

34:04.334 --> 34:06.575
I can't have you risking
your life, other people's lives.

34:06.711 --> 34:10.044
It's too much.

34:10.173 --> 34:11.288
- We can get a cabin.

34:11.424 --> 34:13.085
- It's all too risky.

34:13.218 --> 34:16.756
- No, no, no.
Baby.

34:16.888 --> 34:18.628
I don't care.

34:18.765 --> 34:20.426
I don't want to lose you.

34:24.437 --> 34:25.688
- Promise.

34:30.694 --> 34:32.559
Promise me.

